YII-Ebudget
-----------
IMPORTANT:This is my free time and not profit project, so I may not update frequently. Thanks for checking this application

- The main purpose of this cool application is to experiment the power and features of Yii framework. 
- This small application can manage your daily budget.

Application Features
--------------------
- Custom query pagination
- Flash message -  display success/failure messages in site top section with flash style <http://www.yiiframework.com/wiki/21/how-to-work-with-flash-messages/>
- Records group manage - Wordpress like option
- Database driven config - Handling site settings with database <http://www.yiiframework.com/extension/settings/>

Installation Instructions
-------------------------
gii tool password: 123456

database name: ebudget
database username: root
database password: 